sections.body:
`queryString` has the following syntax:

```javascript
{
  "$search": {
     "index": <index name>, // optional, defaults to "default"
     "queryString": {
        "defaultPath": "<default-field-to-search>",
        "query": "(<field-to-search>: (<search-values>) AND|OR (<search-values>)) AND|OR (<search-values>)"
     }
  }
}
```

